name: Brown County Music Center

boxOfficeInfo.openHoursDetail: Wednesday-Friday 10:00 a.m.-5:00p.m. Saturday - Tuesdays: Open only on event days (4p.m. until 30 minutes after headliner begins).
boxOfficeInfo.willCallDetail: Will call will be available 10 days before the event.

parkingDetail: Preferred Parking $20.00 (Paved lot, Lined spaces, Close to the venue) General Parking $10.00 (Gravel Lot, First come, First served)
accessibleSeatingDetail: 2,017 seat venue with accessible seating available marked in the venue

generalInfo.generalRule: Doors open to the venue 90 minutes before the show. Security check point. No weapons, including knives. Clear bag policy - bags/purses larger than 6 in.x 9 in. not permitted. NO Re-entry.
